It is the solution to find is the given array is non decreasing array or not  
EXAMPLE Input: [4, 2, 3]
Output: true

SOLUTION:
class Solution {
    public boolean nonDecreasingArray(int[] nums) {
        int count=0;
        int n=nums.length;
        for(int i=1;i<n;i++){
            if(nums[i]<nums[i-1]){
                count++;
                if(count>1){
                    return false;

                }
                if(i>1 && nums[i]<nums[i-2]){
                    nums[i]=nums[i-1];
                }
            }
        }
        return true;
    }
}
